ter; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Refract\" target=\"_blank\">Refract</a><br />\n\tRefract means the light is bent due to the density change of the medium. What is refracted? How is it refracted? Where does the refraction take place?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They were amazed by the refraction... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) difference between refract and reflect<br />\n\t2) light refracted, creating a mirage<br />\n\t3) fiber optics and index of refraction<br />\n\t4) white light is refracted to create the rainbow <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/spectrum\" target=\"_blank\">spectrum</a><br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tDoug was not aware of the brightening sky, not until the first rays of the rising sun came through the window and refracted. From his peripheral vision, he could see light shimmering. Thinking it was the rising sun, he paid it no mind. All Doug knew was that he had to work even faster. His eyes were strained, but not enough to bother him. He closed his eyes briefly and pressed on the bridge of his nose. In the few hours he had, Doug managed to narrow it down to a small batch of files.</p>\n<p>\n\